data.description: WOW, 10k price reduction. This Beautiful spacious 5 bedroom, 4 bath home has plenty of space for everyone.  Situated on an oversized corner lot in a cul-de-sac gives many options for outdoor space as well.  The island kitchen and sink will make working in the kitchen a breeze.  It boasts a primary bedroom on first floor with walk in closet and the loft has a projector and screen for television viewing. Stay cool all summer long with refrigerated air and with the solar you won't have to worry about high summer electric bills and breaking the bank.  Schedule your showing today.
